title: Ebro In The Morning - Michael Rapaport VS. Rosenberg
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 10/30.

Actor & Comedian - Michael Rapaport stepped up to Ebro in the Morning and had a lengthy, and sometimes heated conversation about politics, Kevin Durant, Alec Baldwin, and much more.
